text: Ilchigulovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Ilchigulovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 242 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 75 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Ilchigulovo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
